      "date": "2026-07-03",
      "title": "A quiet Saturday",
      "html": "<p>Slept in, made coffee slowly, sat on the balcony for an hour doing nothing. It felt like the first real pause in weeks.</p>",
      "mood": "good",
      "createdAt": 2026070300000
    },
    {
      "id": "7344f69a",
      "date": "2026-07-01",
      "title": "Rough day at work",
      "html": "<p>Missed a deadline and felt awful about it all evening. Rohit called right when I needed it and just let me vent.</p>",
      "mood": "low",
      "createdAt": 2026070100000
    },
    {
      "id": "56525232",
      "date": "2026-06-29",
      "title": "",
      "html": "<p>Went for a run this morning, first one in three weeks. Legs are angry but head is clear.</p>",
